parameters: \n<Soldier>I cannot leave my post! And I can't let a stranger
\n<Soldier>But... If you can find my partner in Traveler's Hub
and give this letter to him, I can let you pass.
\n<Soldier>I know what you're thinking! You can just throw this
away and say you did it, so I may have to ask you more than that.
\n<Soldier>Ask his favorite food, that will be your password for me to
\n<Soldier>Well, that's nice! Now, do you know his favorite food?
\n<Soldier>What is wrong with you? Get out of here!
\n<Soldier>Hmmm! It seems you threw the letter.
